    "• Expert-written prompts.",
    "All prompts in AdvancedIF are carefully written by human experts.",
    "In particular, in the multi-turn conversation category, human experts interacted with LLM to provide an appropriate prompt according to the model response at the last turn, reflecting the real user engagement behavior and style.",
    "• Expert-written rubrics.",
    "Each prompt is paired with a rubric, which was first written by a human expert and then went through multiple rounds of human review, reflecting granular criteria of the prompt."
